title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - New updates also for non beta participants
description:
In this video we will have a look at two updates which have been released for MSFS. One of them updates the World Hub and AIRAC and is available for all simmers while the other update is specifically for Sim Update 15 beta testers using the Xbox to play MSFS.
